<sect1 id="index_1autotoc_md6">
<title>Installation</title>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md7">
<title>C++</title>
<para>The binary packages are hosted using <ulink url="https://github.com/open-space-collective/open-space-toolkit-io/releases">GitHub Releases</ulink>:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Runtime libraries: <computeroutput>open-space-toolkit-io-X.Y.Z-1.x86_64-runtime</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>C++ headers: <computeroutput>open-space-toolkit-io-X.Y.Z-1.x86_64-devel</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Python bindings: <computeroutput>open-space-toolkit-io-X.Y.Z-1.x86_64-python</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<sect3 id="index_1autotoc_md8">
<title>Debian / Ubuntu</title>
<para>After downloading the relevant <computeroutput>.deb</computeroutput> binary packages, install:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">apt<sp/>install<sp/>open-space-toolkit-io-*.deb</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect3>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="index_1autotoc_md9">
<title>Python</title>
<para>Install from <ulink url="https://pypi.org/project/open-space-toolkit-io/">PyPI</ulink>:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">pip<sp/>install<sp/>open-space-toolkit-io</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
